9</a>, 6. Lombard War.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins199832–33-36" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins199832–33-36"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECollins199832–33_36-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins199832–33-36" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFCollins1998" id="mwBY8">Collins 1998</a>, pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZA"> </span>32–33.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard19993._Charlemagne's_Accession-37" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard19993._Charlemagne's_Accession-37"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEEinhard19993._Charlemagne's_Accession_37-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard19993._Charlemagne's_Accession-37" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFEinhard1999" id="mwBZE">Einhard 1999</a>, 3. Charlemagne's Accession.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard,_putative741–829Year_768-38" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard,_putative741–829Year_768-38"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEEinhard,_putative741–829Year_768_38-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEEinhard,_putative741–829Year_768-38" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFEinhard,_putative741–829" id="mwBZI">Einhard, putative <span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZM">&amp;</span> 741–829</a>, Year 768.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins198732-39" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins198732-39"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECollins198732_39-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins198732-39" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFCollins1987" id="mwBZQ">Collins 1987</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZU"> </span>32.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987105-40" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987105-40"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECollins1987105_40-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987105-40" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFCollins1987" id="mwBZY">Collins 1987</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZc"> </span>105.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEDouglassBilbao200536–37-41" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEDouglassBilbao200536–37-41"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEDouglassBilbao200536–37_41-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEDouglassBilbao200536–37-41" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFDouglassBilbao2005" id="mwBZg">Douglass <span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZk">&amp;</span> Bilbao 2005</a>, pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZo"> </span>36–37.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987100-42" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987100-42"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-FOOTNOTECollins1987100_42-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTECollins1987100-42" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFCollins1987" id="mwBZs">Collins 1987</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwBZw"> </span>100.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-43" id="cite_note-43"><a href="./Charlemagne#cite_ref-43" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-43" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Charlemagne#CITEREFCollins2004" about="#mwt90" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"harvnb","href":"./Template:Harvnb"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Collins"},"2":{"wt":"2004"},"pp":{