<li><cite class="citation book">Sypeck, Jeff (2006). <i>Becoming Charlemagne: Europe, Baghdad, and The Empires of A.D. 800</i>. New York: Ecco/HarperCollins. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Special:BookSources/978-0-06-079706-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-06-079706-5">978-0-06-079706-5</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Becoming+Charlemagne%3A+Europe%2C+Baghdad%2C+and+The+Empires+of+A.D.+800&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pub=Ecco%2FHarperCollins&amp;rft.date=2006&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-06-079706-5&amp;rft.aulast=Sypeck&amp;rft.aufirst=Jeff&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACharlemagne" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt958" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}'/></li>
