2" data-file-height="236" data-file-type="bitmap" height="102" width="100" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Cuninpert_688_700_king_of_the_Lombard_minted_in_Milan.jpg/200px-Cuninpert_688_700_king_of_the_Lombard_minted_in_Milan.jpg 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c3/Cuninpert_688_700_king_of_the_Lombard_minted_in_Milan.jpg/150px-Cuninpert_688_700_king_of_the_Lombard_minted_in_Milan.jpg 1.5x"/></a><figcaption>Cunipert (688-700).</figcaption></figure></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="width:1%"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ostrogoths" title="Ostrogoths">Ostrogoths</a></th><td class="navbox-list navbox-even hlist" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px"><div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
