<div role="navigation" class="navbox" aria-labelledby="Heads_of_state_of_France" style="padding:3px" about="#mwt949" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Monarchs of France","href":"./Template:Monarchs_of_France"},"params":{},"i":0}}]}' id="mwB_M"><table class="nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner" style="border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit"><tbody><tr><th scope="col" class="navbox-title" colspan="2"><div class="plainlinks hlist navbar mini"><ul><li class="nv-view"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template:Heads_of_state_of_France" title="Template:Heads of state of France"><abbr title="View this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">v</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-talk"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Template_talk:Heads_of_state_of_France" title="Template talk:Heads of state of France"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Heads_of_state_of_France&amp;action=edit"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="Heads_of_state_of_France" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./List_of_heads_of_state_of_France" title="List of heads of state of France">Heads of state of France</a></div></th></tr><tr><td class="navbox-abovebelow" colspan="2"><div id="Recognized_as_Francia_from_481_to_843_–_Recognized_as_West_Francia_from_843_to_987_–_Recognized_as_France_from_987_to_presentStyled_President_of_the_Republic_after_1871,_except_from_1940_to_1944_(Chief_of_State)_and_1944_to_1947_(Chairman_of_the_Provisional_Government).&amp;#10;Detailed_monarch_family_tree_&amp;#124;_Simplified_monarch_family_tree">Recognized as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Francia" title="Francia">Francia</a> from 481 to 843 – Recognized as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./West_Francia" title="West Francia">West Francia</a> from 843 to 987 – Recognized as <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./France" title="France">France</a> from 987 to present<br/>Styled <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./President_of_France" title="President of France">President of the Republic</a> after 1871, except from 1940 to 1944 (Chief of State) and 1944 to 1947 (Chairman of the Provisional Government).<br/>
